metadata.name: Eyes on ETH
metadata.description:
When the news hit, the NFT rush started. EYELIENS from all over space raced to chase, poke, pull, twist, turn, stretch and try everything to understand the nature of the ETHeric creatures. The evolution to a new era had begun. The high-speed and rapid morphing, multiplication, expansion, and contraction, allowed eyeliens to evolve new and creative ways of living, thinking, collaborating, and working with one another. There was no going back now.
